{
  "video_id": "RPjqPHCMJHU",
  "title": "Rose Goslinga: Crop insurance, an idea worth seeding",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12465.0,
      "end_time": 15722.0,
      "text": "In Kenya, 1984 is known"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15722.0,
      "end_time": 18333.0,
      "text": "as the year of the cup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18333.0,
      "end_time": 20753.0,
      "text": "or the goro goro."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20753.0,
      "end_time": 23671.0,
      "text": "The goro goro is a cup used to measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23671.0,
      "end_time": 26980.0,
      "text": "two kilograms of maize flower on the market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26981.0,
      "end_time": 30121.0,
      "text": "and the maize flower is used to make ugali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30121.0,
      "end_time": 34770.0,
      "text": "a polenta-like cake that is eaten together with vegetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34780.0,
      "end_time": 36393.0,
      "text": "Both the maize and the vegetables are grown"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36393.0,
      "end_time": 38518.0,
      "text": "on most Kenyan farms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38518.0,
      "end_time": 40791.0,
      "text": "which means that most families can feed themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40791.0,
      "end_time": 42971.0,
      "text": "from their own farm."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42972.0,
      "end_time": 46900.0,
      "text": "One goro goro can feed three meals"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46900.0,
      "end_time": 48881.0,
      "text": "for an average family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48881.0,
      "end_time": 51970.0,
      "text": "and in 1984, the whole harvest"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51970.0,
      "end_time": 55141.0,
      "text": "could fit in one goro goro."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55142.0,
      "end_time": 57992.0,
      "text": "It was and still is one of the worst droughts"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57992.0,
      "end_time": 60635.0,
      "text": "in living memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60635.0,
      "end_time": 63594.0,
      "text": "Now today, I insure farmers against droughts"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63594.0,
      "end_time": 65655.0,
      "text": "like those in the year of the cup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65655.0,
      "end_time": 70641.0,
      "text": "or to be more specific, I insure the rains."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70641.0,
      "end_time": 73900.0,
      "text": "I come from a family of missionaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73900.0,
      "end_time": 75241.0,
      "text": "who built hospitals in Indonesia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75241.0,
      "end_time": 77518.0,
      "text": "and my father built a psychiatric hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77518.0,
      "end_time": 78774.0,
      "text": "in Tanzania."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78774.0,
      "end_time": 81875.0,
      "text": "This is me, age five, in front of that hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81875.0,
      "end_time": 84196.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think they thought I&#39;d grow up"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84196.0,
      "end_time": 87161.0,
      "text": "to sell insurance. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87162.0,
      "end_time": 90203.0,
      "text": "So let me tell you how that happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90203.0,
      "end_time": 91920.0,
      "text": "In 2008, I was working"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91920.0,
      "end_time": 94204.0,
      "text": "for the Ministry of Agriculture of Rwanda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94204.0,
      "end_time": 96199.0,
      "text": "and my boss had just been promoted"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96200.0,
      "end_time": 97607.0,
      "text": "to become the minister."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97607.0,
      "end_time": 99495.0,
      "text": "She launched an ambitious plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99495.0,
      "end_time": 101824.0,
      "text": "to start a green revolution in her country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101824.0,
      "end_time": 103444.0,
      "text": "and before we knew it, we were importing"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103444.0,
      "end_time": 105737.0,
      "text": "tons of fertilizer and seed"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105737.0,
      "end_time": 108461.0,
      "text": "and telling farmers how to apply that fertilizer"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108462.0,
      "end_time": 109997.0,
      "text": "and plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109997.0,
      "end_time": 111890.0,
      "text": "A couple of weeks later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111890.0,
      "end_time": 114603.0,
      "text": "the International Monetary Fund visited us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114603.0,
      "end_time": 116133.0,
      "text": "and asked my minister,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116133.0,
      "end_time": 118945.0,
      "text": "\"Minister, it&#39;s great that you want to help farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118945.0,
      "end_time": 123118.0,
      "text": "reach food security, but what if it doesn&#39;t rain?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 123118.0,
      "end_time": 125267.0,
      "text": "My minister answered proudly"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 125267.0,
      "end_time": 127280.0,
      "text": "and somewhat defiantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127281.0,
      "end_time": 131871.0,
      "text": "\"I am going to pray for rain.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131871.0,
      "end_time": 135710.0,
      "text": "That ended the discussion."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135710.0,
      "end_time": 137225.0,
      "text": "On the way back to the ministry in the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 137225.0,
      "end_time": 139305.0,
      "text": "she turned around to me and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139306.0,
      "end_time": 141376.0,
      "text": "\"Rose, you&#39;ve always been interested in finance."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 141376.0,
      "end_time": 144515.0,
      "text": "Go find us some insurance.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144515.0,
      "end_time": 146552.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been six years since,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146552.0,
      "end_time": 148542.0,
      "text": "and last year I was fortunate enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 148542.0,
      "end_time": 150480.0,
      "text": "to be part of a team that insured"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150480.0,
      "end_time": 153953.0,
      "text": "over 185,000 farmers in Kenya and Rwanda"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 153953.0,
      "end_time": 155890.0,
      "text": "against drought."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 155890.0,
      "end_time": 157970.0,
      "text": "They owned an average of half an acre"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 157970.0,
      "end_time": 161423.0,
      "text": "and paid on average two Euros in premium."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 161423.0,
      "end_time": 163800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s microinsurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 163800.0,
      "end_time": 165855.0,
      "text": "Now, traditional insurance doesn&#39;t work"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165855.0,
      "end_time": 167768.0,
      "text": "with two to three Euros of premium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167768.0,
      "end_time": 170675.0,
      "text": "because traditional insurance relies on farm visits."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 170675.0,
      "end_time": 172617.0,
      "text": "A farmer here in Germany would be visited"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 172617.0,
      "end_time": 175102.0,
      "text": "for the start of the season, halfway through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 175102.0,
      "end_time": 177589.0,
      "text": "and at the end, and again if there was a loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 177589.0,
      "end_time": 180995.0,
      "text": "to estimate the damages."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 180995.0,
      "end_time": 184130.0,
      "text": "For a small-scale farmer in the middle of Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 184130.0,
      "end_time": 185959.0,
      "text": "the maths of doing those visits"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 185959.0,
      "end_time": 189300.0,
      "text": "simply don&#39;t add up."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 189300.0,
      "end_time": 192871.0,
      "text": "So instead, we rely on technology and data."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 192871.0,
      "end_time": 195770.0,
      "text": "This satellite measures"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 195770.0,
      "end_time": 197239.0,
      "text": "whether there were clouds or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 197239.0,
      "end_time": 198407.0,
      "text": "because think about it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 198407.0,
      "end_time": 203109.0,
      "text": "If there are clouds, then you might have some rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 203109.0,
      "end_time": 204808.0,
      "text": "but if there are no clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 204808.0,
      "end_time": 207659.0,
      "text": "then it&#39;s actually impossible for it to rain."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 207659.0,
      "end_time": 209939.0,
      "text": "These images show the onset of the rains"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 209939.0,
      "end_time": 211793.0,
      "text": "this season in Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 211794.0,
      "end_time": 213830.0,
      "text": "You see that around March 6,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 213830.0,
      "end_time": 216935.0,
      "text": "the clouds move in and then disappear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 216935.0,
      "end_time": 218963.0,
      "text": "and then around the March 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 218963.0,
      "end_time": 222213.0,
      "text": "the clouds really move in."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 222213.0,
      "end_time": 225140.0,
      "text": "That, and those clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 225140.0,
      "end_time": 228280.0,
      "text": "were the onset of the rains this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 228280.0,
      "end_time": 230715.0,
      "text": "This satellite covers the whole of Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230715.0,
      "end_time": 233632.0,
      "text": "and goes back as far as 1984,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 233632.0,
      "end_time": 235980.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s important, because if you know"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 235980.0,
      "end_time": 238421.0,
      "text": "how many times a place has had a drought"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 238421.0,
      "end_time": 240370.0,
      "text": "in the last 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 240370.0,
      "end_time": 242200.0,
      "text": "you can make a pretty good estimate"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 242200.0,
      "end_time": 244957.0,
      "text": "what the chances are of drought in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 244957.0,
      "end_time": 247700.0,
      "text": "and that means that you can put a price tag"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 247700.0,
      "end_time": 249760.0,
      "text": "on the risk of drought."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 249760.0,
      "end_time": 252155.0,
      "text": "The data alone isn&#39;t enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 252156.0,
      "end_time": 254641.0,
      "text": "We devise agronomic algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 254641.0,
      "end_time": 258334.0,
      "text": "which tell us how much rainfall a crop needs and when."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 258334.0,
      "end_time": 260748.0,
      "text": "For example, for maize at planting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 260749.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263144.0,
      "text": "you need to have two days of rain"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 263144.0,
      "end_time": 265000.0,
      "text": "for farmers to plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 265000.0,
      "end_time": 267194.0,
      "text": "and then it needs to rain once every two weeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 267194.0,
      "end_time": 269673.0,
      "text": "for the crop to properly germinate."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 269673.0,
      "end_time": 272998.0,
      "text": "After that, you need rain every three weeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 272998.0,
      "end_time": 275901.0,
      "text": "for the crop to form its leaves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 275901.0,
      "end_time": 278667.0,
      "text": "whereas at flowering, you need it to rain more frequently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 278667.0,
      "end_time": 282527.0,
      "text": "about once every 10 days for the crop to form its cob."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 282527.0,
      "end_time": 284320.0,
      "text": "At the end of the season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 284320.0,
      "end_time": 286244.0,
      "text": "you actually don&#39;t want it to rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 286244.0,
      "end_time": 289795.0,
      "text": "because rains then can damage the crop."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 289795.0,
      "end_time": 293150.0,
      "text": "Devising such a cover is difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 293150.0,
      "end_time": 295460.0,
      "text": "but it turned out the real challenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 295460.0,
      "end_time": 299574.0,
      "text": "was selling insurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299574.0,
      "end_time": 302610.0,
      "text": "We set ourselves a modest target"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 302610.0,
      "end_time": 306610.0,
      "text": "of 500 farmers insured after our first season."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 306610.0,
      "end_time": 308631.0,
      "text": "After a couple of months&#39; intense marketing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 308631.0,
      "end_time": 310450.0,
      "text": "we had signed up the grand total"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 310450.0,
      "end_time": 314108.0,
      "text": "of 185 farmers."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 314108.0,
      "end_time": 317300.0,
      "text": "I was disappointed and confounded."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 317300.0,
      "end_time": 318683.0,
      "text": "Everybody kept telling me that farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 318684.0,
      "end_time": 321267.0,
      "text": "wanted insurance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 321267.0,
      "end_time": 324264.0,
      "text": "but our prime customers simply weren&#39;t buying."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324264.0,
      "end_time": 326928.0,
      "text": "They were waiting to see what would happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 326928.0,
      "end_time": 329677.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t trust insurance companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 329677.0,
      "end_time": 331963.0,
      "text": "or thought, \"I&#39;ve managed for so many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 331963.0,
      "end_time": 335720.0,
      "text": "Why would I buy insurance now?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 335720.0,
      "end_time": 338102.0,
      "text": "Now many of you know microcredit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 338102.0,
      "end_time": 341596.0,
      "text": "the method of providing small loans to poor people"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 341596.0,
      "end_time": 343598.0,
      "text": "pioneered by Muhammad Yunus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 343598.0,
      "end_time": 345119.0,
      "text": "who won the Nobel Peace Prize"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 345119.0,
      "end_time": 347268.0,
      "text": "for his work with the Grameen Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 347268.0,
      "end_time": 349751.0,
      "text": "Turns out, selling microcredit"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 349752.0,
      "end_time": 353153.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t the same as selling insurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 353153.0,
      "end_time": 357380.0,
      "text": "For credit, a farmer needs to earn the trust of a bank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 357380.0,
      "end_time": 360982.0,
      "text": "and if it succeeds, the bank will advance him money."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 360982.0,
      "end_time": 363910.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an attractive proposition."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 363910.0,
      "end_time": 366337.0,
      "text": "For insurance, the farmer needs to trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 366337.0,
      "end_time": 367878.0,
      "text": "the insurance company, and needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 367879.0,
      "end_time": 371103.0,
      "text": "to advance the insurance company money."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 371103.0,
      "end_time": 374470.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very different value proposition."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 374470.0,
      "end_time": 377159.0,
      "text": "And so the uptick of insurance has been slow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 377159.0,
      "end_time": 379735.0,
      "text": "with so far only 4.4 percent of Africans"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 379735.0,
      "end_time": 382288.0,
      "text": "taking up insurance in 2012,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 382288.0,
      "end_time": 384280.0,
      "text": "and half of that number is in one country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 384280.0,
      "end_time": 386323.0,
      "text": "South Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 386323.0,
      "end_time": 387969.0,
      "text": "We tried for some years"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 387970.0,
      "end_time": 390421.0,
      "text": "selling insurance directly to farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 390421.0,
      "end_time": 392420.0,
      "text": "with very high marketing cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 392420.0,
      "end_time": 395506.0,
      "text": "and very limited success."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 395506.0,
      "end_time": 397460.0,
      "text": "Then we realized that there were many organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 397460.0,
      "end_time": 400169.0,
      "text": "working with farmers:"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 400169.0,
      "end_time": 403606.0,
      "text": "seed companies, microfinance institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 403606.0,
      "end_time": 405552.0,
      "text": "mobile phone companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 405552.0,
      "end_time": 406874.0,
      "text": "government agencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 406874.0,
      "end_time": 409624.0,
      "text": "They were all providing loans to farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 409624.0,
      "end_time": 412246.0,
      "text": "and often, just before they&#39;d finalize the loan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 412246.0,
      "end_time": 414346.0,
      "text": "the farmer would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 414346.0,
      "end_time": 416498.0,
      "text": "\"But what if it doesn&#39;t rain?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 416498.0,
      "end_time": 419965.0,
      "text": "How do you expect me to repay my loan?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 419965.0,
      "end_time": 422420.0,
      "text": "Many of these organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 422420.0,
      "end_time": 423659.0,
      "text": "were taking on the risk themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 423660.0,
      "end_time": 425628.0,
      "text": "simply hoping that that year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 425628.0,
      "end_time": 427990.0,
      "text": "the worst wouldn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 427990.0,
      "end_time": 429996.0,
      "text": "Most of the organizations, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 429996.0,
      "end_time": 432318.0,
      "text": "were limiting their growth in agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 432319.0,
      "end_time": 434991.0,
      "text": "They couldn&#39;t take on this kind of risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 434991.0,
      "end_time": 438714.0,
      "text": "These organizations became our customers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 438714.0,
      "end_time": 441913.0,
      "text": "and when combining credit and insurance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 441913.0,
      "end_time": 444632.0,
      "text": "interesting things can happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 444632.0,
      "end_time": 448200.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you one more story."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 448200.0,
      "end_time": 451870.0,
      "text": "At the start of February 2012 in western Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 451870.0,
      "end_time": 454869.0,
      "text": "the rains started, and they started early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 454869.0,
      "end_time": 457940.0,
      "text": "and when rains start early, farmers are encouraged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 457940.0,
      "end_time": 461506.0,
      "text": "because it usually means that the season is going to be good."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 461506.0,
      "end_time": 464261.0,
      "text": "So they took out loans and planted."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 464262.0,
      "end_time": 465752.0,
      "text": "For the next three weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 465752.0,
      "end_time": 468600.0,
      "text": "there wasn&#39;t a single drop of rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 468600.0,
      "end_time": 470624.0,
      "text": "and the crops that had germinated so well"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 470624.0,
      "end_time": 473937.0,
      "text": "shriveled and died."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 473937.0,
      "end_time": 476692.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d insured the loans of a microfinance institution"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 476692.0,
      "end_time": 477812.0,
      "text": "that had provided those loans"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 477812.0,
      "end_time": 481360.0,
      "text": "to about 6,000 farmers in that area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 481360.0,
      "end_time": 482650.0,
      "text": "and we called them up and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 482650.0,
      "end_time": 484349.0,
      "text": "\"Look, we know about the drought."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 484350.0,
      "end_time": 486140.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got you."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 486140.0,
      "end_time": 490327.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll give you 200,000 Euros at the end of the season.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 490327.0,
      "end_time": 492126.0,
      "text": "They said, \"Wow, that&#39;s great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 492126.0,
      "end_time": 494251.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;ll be late."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 494252.0,
      "end_time": 496435.0,
      "text": "Could you give us the money now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 496435.0,
      "end_time": 498865.0,
      "text": "Then these farmers can still replant"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 498865.0,
      "end_time": 502442.0,
      "text": "and can get a harvest this season.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 502442.0,
      "end_time": 504523.0,
      "text": "So we convinced our insurance partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 504523.0,
      "end_time": 507898.0,
      "text": "and later that April, these farmers replanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 507898.0,
      "end_time": 510692.0,
      "text": "We took the idea of replanting to a seed company"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 510692.0,
      "end_time": 512802.0,
      "text": "and convinced them to price the cost of insurance"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 512802.0,
      "end_time": 514941.0,
      "text": "into every bag of seed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 514941.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516920.00000000006,
      "text": "and in every bag, we packed a card"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 516919.0,
      "end_time": 518493.0,
      "text": "that had a number on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 518494.0,
      "end_time": 520476.0,
      "text": "and when the farmers would open the card,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 520476.0,
      "end_time": 522477.0,
      "text": "they&#39;d text in that number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 522477.0,
      "end_time": 523850.0,
      "text": "and that number would actually help us"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 523850.0,
      "end_time": 525225.0,
      "text": "to locate the farmer"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 525225.0,
      "end_time": 528349.0,
      "text": "and allocate them to a satellite pixel."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 528349.0,
      "end_time": 530891.0,
      "text": "A satellite would then measure the rainfall"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 530891.0,
      "end_time": 532424.0,
      "text": "for the next three weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 532424.0,
      "end_time": 534154.0,
      "text": "and if it didn&#39;t rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 534154.0,
      "end_time": 537560.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d replace their seed."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 537560.0,
      "end_time": 538800.0,
      "text": "One of the first —"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 538800.0,
      "end_time": 544220.0,
      "text": "(Applause) — Hold on, I&#39;m not there!"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 544230.0,
      "end_time": 547180.0,
      "text": "One of the first beneficiaries of this replanting guarantee"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 547180.0,
      "end_time": 549396.0,
      "text": "was Bosco Mwinyi."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 549396.0,
      "end_time": 552870.0,
      "text": "We visited his farm later that August,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 552870.0,
      "end_time": 555643.0,
      "text": "and I wish I could show you the smile on his face"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 555643.0,
      "end_time": 558107.0,
      "text": "when he showed us his harvest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 558107.0,
      "end_time": 559740.0,
      "text": "because it warmed my heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 559740.0,
      "end_time": 561678.0,
      "text": "and it made me realize why selling insurance"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 561678.0,
      "end_time": 564388.0,
      "text": "can be a good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 564388.0,
      "end_time": 565936.0,
      "text": "But you know, he insisted"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 565936.0,
      "end_time": 568890.0,
      "text": "that we get his whole harvest in the picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 568890.0,
      "end_time": 572753.0,
      "text": "so we had to zoom out a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 572753.0,
      "end_time": 575982.0,
      "text": "Insurance secured his harvest that season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 575982.0,
      "end_time": 578502.0,
      "text": "and I believe that today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 578502.0,
      "end_time": 581685.0,
      "text": "we have all the tools to enable African farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 581685.0,
      "end_time": 584452.0,
      "text": "to take control of their own destiny."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 584452.0,
      "end_time": 585951.0,
      "text": "No more years of the cup."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 585951.0,
      "end_time": 589289.0,
      "text": "Instead, I am looking forward to, at least somehow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 589289.0,
      "end_time": 591944.0,
      "text": "the year of the insurance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 591945.0,
      "end_time": 594648.0,
      "text": "or the year of the great harvest."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 594648.0,
      "end_time": 597850.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 597850.0,
      "end_time": 599464.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}